-- BAE Nears Deal to Sell 30 Hawk Jets to Saudi Arabia, Times Says
-- B y   T h o m a s   B i e s h e u v e l
-- 2012-05-06T13:12:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-06/bae-close-to-selling-30-hawk-jets-to-saudi-arabia-times-says.html
BAE Systems Plc (BA/)  is close to agreeing
to a 500 million pounds ($808 million) sale to  Saudi Arabia  of
as many as 30 Hawk training aircraft, the Sunday Times reported,
without saying where it got the information.  The order will probably be completed in the next few
months, the newspaper said.  A BAE spokeswoman declined to comment when contacted by
telephone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Biesheuvel in London at 
